body_html: Hi, @peterjc123 , Thank you very much. I found that the error is caused by the original command "from ._ext import roi_pooling". It should be "from _ext import roi_pooling" in \roi_pooling dir. The difference is on the character " . " before "_ext".

body: Hi, @peterjc123 , Thank you very much. I found that the error is caused by the original command "from ._ext import roi_pooling". It should be "from _ext import roi_pooling" in \roi_pooling dir. The difference is on the character " . " before "_ext".
